original_title: American Indian Comedy Slam: Goin Native No Reservations Needed
overview: In the spirit of the Kings of Comedy, no reservations needed for this "Goin' Native" stand-up comedy event. Hosted by Legendary Charlie Hill, starring Larry Omaha, Howie Miller, Marc Yaffee, Jim Rule, Vaughn Eagle Bear and JR Redwater. Presented by Laugh Out Loud Flix
title: American Indian Comedy Slam: Goin Native No Reservations Needed
